  "title": "Medidor ElNet MC-1 | Control Applications",
  "description": "Sistema trifásico de medida de energía.\nHasta 3 fases para medición de energía.\nPrecisión de medición 0,2% (0,1% en pedido especial).\n1600 muestras por ola.\nVisualización continua de datos de medición.\nRecopilación de datos energéticos durante 4 meses.\nReloj con tipos de cambio de divisas.\nMedición de armonías hasta la armonía 64.\nSoporte para múltiples idiomas.\nRS485 canal de comunicación.\nSoporte para protocolos de comunicación MODBUS/BACNET.\nPantalla a color de 320X240 de alta calidad.\nVisualización gráfica de forma de onda.\nInstalación sencilla sobre carril DIN.\nTCP/IP comunicación, soporte por correo electrónico\nRecopilación de datos estructurados.",
  "og_image": "/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-8-3.png",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>ElNet MC-1 counter</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p><span><span>Three-phase system for measuring energy.<br/>Up to 3 phases for energy measurement.<br/>Measurement accuracy 0.2% (0.1% on special order).<br/>1600 samples per wave.<br/>Continuous display of measurement data.<br/>Collecting energy data for 4 months.<br/>Clock with foreign exchange rates.<br/>Measuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.<br/>Support for multiple languages.<br/>RS485 communication channel.<br/>Support for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.<br/>High quality 320X240 color screen.<br/>Graphical waveform display.<br/>Simple installation on a DIN rail.<br/>TCP/IP communication, e-mail support<br/>Structured data collection.</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>Energy meters</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>Related products -</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h1>electrical systems</h1></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>-</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>✔</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>Control Applications Ltd</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>making contact</p>\n<p>Phone: +972-3-6474998​</p>\n<p>Fax: +972-3-6474598</p>\n<p><span>Email:<a href=\"mailto:cal@ddc.co.il\">cal@ddc.co.il</a></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>opening hours</p>\n<p>Control Applications Ltd</p>\n<p>Sunday - Thursday</p>\n<p>08:00 - 17:00</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>address</p>\n<p>25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv</p>\n<p>6971035</p>\n<p>Israel</p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p>© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd</p></div>\n<figure class=\"content-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/screen-shot-2021-01-20-at-22-15.png\" alt=\"Screen%20Shot%202021-01-20%20at%2022.15_\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-8-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-6-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-7-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-8-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-9-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-10-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/uniart-software-content-11-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-8-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-10-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-12-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-14-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-control-content-8-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"/></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-image\"><img src=\"/assets/images/power-meters-c